nodes.text: Fadime was a Nikto female who was a pilot, known as Hound Six, in the New Republic's Hound Squadron. During the Attack on the Hellion's Dare, Fadime helped defend the frigate as they fled into the Oridol Cluster. When Hound Leader Stanislok was killed, Fadime assumed some of his duties, including leading the squadron at the tactical board. Fadime was killed shortly after by the 204th Imperial Fighter Wing.
